title: Fabulous Finds BETA - New Hidden Object Puzzle[Wendy99]
description:
Fabulous Finds BETA Oberon Media



Sort, Sell, Splurge!
 Three great games become a brand new, one-of-a-kind experience where seek & find is just the beginning.
 Fabulous Finds brings players a unique combination of hidden objects, yard sale brainteasers and room renovating fun!
 This exciting adventure is filled with delightful discoveries and a charming connection to your past - that could help pave the path to your future!



 After installing use the patch for making full BETA copy the patch to the game directory and overwrite to existing one.
